simgui (0.5.4-1) unstable; urgency=high

  * Fix startup timeout: network reconnect, ICCID scan, and sudo check
    now run in a background thread. GUI appears instantly.
  * Share indicator shows grey at startup, updates when background
    thread completes.

 -- SimGUI Developers <simgui@example.com>  Sun, 15 Mar 2026 21:00:00 +0100

simgui (0.5.3-1) unstable; urgency=high

  * CRITICAL: mount() now tracks already-mounted shares in _active_mounts.
    Previously, shares left mounted across app restarts were invisible to
    get_active_mount_paths(), causing ICCID index to never scan and share
    indicator to show disconnected even though share was mounted.
  * reconnect_saved() delegates to mount() instead of short-circuiting.
  * Periodic share poll no longer duplicates _refresh_share_indicator at
    startup (removed redundant call that could add latency).

 -- SimGUI Developers <simgui@example.com>  Sun, 15 Mar 2026 19:20:00 +0100

simgui (0.5.2-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix: Blank card no longer overwrites pre-loaded CSV data.
  * Fix: Action status text is now selectable and copyable.
  * Fix: Share indicator refreshes after file browse + periodic 30s poll.
  * Added workflow plan document (docs/WORKFLOW_PLAN.md).
  * Improved blank-card messaging (distinct states for data-ready vs empty).

