simgui (0.5.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Build hash baked into BUILD file — visible in title bar and About.
  * Card Status panel: added ACC, SPN, FPLMN fields read from card.
  * Parse ACC, SPN, FPLMN from pySim-read output.
  * Fix: CSV row selection no longer resets 'Insert SIM' when card present.
