simgui (0.5.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Real pySim integration: authenticate, program with change tracking.
  * pySim included in install.sh (cloned to /opt/pysim with venv).
  * Already-programmed popup with previous IMSI on card detect.
  * ICCID read-only for non-empty cards.
  * Git commit hash shown in title bar.
  * Fix share icon not updating after connect.
  * Fix hardware mode not clearing simulator state.
  * ICCID index caching to avoid re-parsing unchanged files.
  * Auto-artifact per-card CSV on every programming.

