simgui (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * CSV batch editor for SIM card configurations.
  * Card detection and ADM1 authentication via sysmo-usim-tool or pySim.
  * Built-in SIM programmer simulator with 20 real sysmoISIM-SJA5 profiles.
  * ICCID cross-verification safety check before ADM1 authentication.
  * Debian packaging for easy installation.

